org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.api.template

Interface MediationTemplate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.annotation.Annotation

    Main annotation to mark a class as an UltraESB template. This is an class level annotation specifying the main user interface properties as well as the template key used withing the ESB.
    Since:
    2.0.0

    • Method Summary

      Methods

    • Method Detail

      • key

        java.lang.String key()
        Defines the key that is associated with the annotated template, this parameter MUST be specified for the annotation to be valid. This has to be unique among the templates globally as it is used as the template identifier in the ESB
        Returns:
        the template key

      • type

        TemplateType type()
        The type of the template, used to categorize the templates. Mainly used in the user interface designing
        Returns:
        the template type
